data.description: Rare opportunity! Custom built 3 Bed 2 Bath home w/ a bonus/4th bedroom upstairs, & 40x60 workshop all on 19.11+/- acres of pasture & wooded land! Open/Split Floor Plan w/ wood floors in living areas, tile in wet areas. Gas log fireplace. Large kitchen w/ stainless steel appliances. Master Suite w/ 2 walk in closets, jetted tub, tiled shower, & an office/nursery. Utility Room with a utility sink. Gorgeous views from the covered front porch. Covered back porch w/ deck & pergola. Fire pit surrounded by stamped concrete. Workshop w/ 4 roll up doors, 3/4 bath, 40x30 is heated & cooled & 328sqft bonus room upstairs. Lean-to w/ RV hookups for power and water. Bream in pond, deer seen often! See property highlights in documents.
